data.description: Nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, this magnificent residence offers the epitome of spacious and serene suburban living. With an expansive lot that boasts a vast backyard, with a pond view, this home is a haven for those seeking room to breathe, play, and entertain with a huge formal dining area, bar in the screened patio and another living space upstairs. Conveniently located to the interstate, NAS Jax, shopping, restaurants, movie theaters, and much much more! Your future home awaits you, schedule your tour now! All information pertaining to the property is deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Information to be verified by the Buyer.
